snippet: Australian police arrested a Sydney man on Monday as part of operations to disrupt the flow of money and fighters to conflict zones such as those in Iraq and Syria, where dozens of Australians are said to have joined Islamist militant groups....

headline.print_headline: Australian Police Arrest One on Terrorism Financing Charges
headline.main: Australian Police Arrest One on Terrorism Financing Charges

lead_paragraph: Australian police arrested a Sydney man on Monday as part of operations to disrupt the flow of money and fighters to conflict zones such as those in Iraq and Syria, where dozens of Australians are said to have joined Islamist militant groups.
